  "w = P - 2l": "",
  "w = P/2 - l": "",
  "w = (P - 2l)/2": "",
  "Subtract 2l: P - 2l = 2w. Divide by 2: w = (P - 2l)/2. Note: (P - 2l)/2 and P/2 - l are equivalent.": "",
  "Solve for t: d = rt": "",
  "t = d - r": "",
  "t = d/r": "",
  "t = dr": "",
  "t = r/d": "",
  "Divide both sides by r: t = d/r.": "",
  "Solve for b: A = (1/2)bh": "",
