  "Expressed as a decimal": "",
  "Expressed using the other given variables and constants": "",
  "Set equal to zero": "",
  "Expressed as a graph": "",
  "When we solve for y 'in terms of' x, it means y is written as an expression involving x, such as y = 3x + 2.": "",
